在[[聖地牙哥國際漫畫展|聖地牙哥國際漫畫展]]之前，[[執行製片人|執行製片人]]兼[[節目統籌|節目統籌]]{{le|馬克·古根海姆|Marc Guggenheim}}透露本季的主題為「身份認同」<ref name="HR">{{cite web|url=https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/live-feed/arrow-bosses-season-3-secrets-719881|title='Arrow' Bosses Reveal Season 3 Secrets: New Romances, Dark Arcs and Big Surprises|last=Ng|first=Philiana|work=[[The_Hollywood_Reporter|The Hollywood Reporter]]|date=2014-07-23|access-date=2018-07-09|dead-url=no|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180529202656/https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/live-feed/arrow-bosses-season-3-secrets-719881|archive-date=2018-05-29|language=en-US}}</ref>。他與執行製片人{{le|安德魯·克雷斯伯格|Andrew Kreisberg}}表示本季故事的發生時間在上季結尾之後的六個月，在倒敘情節中講述奧利佛被認定死亡之後第三年在香港的經歷，同時展現他與[[阿曼達·華勒|阿曼達·華勒]]的關係<ref name="Pester">{{cite web|url=https://www.eonline.com/uk/news/563386/arrow-at-comic-con-get-scoop-on-a-two-hour-flash-crossover-oliver-and-felicity-s-romance-and-more|title=Arrow at Comic-Con: Get Scoop on a Two-Hour Flash Crossover, Oliver and Felicity's Romance and More!|last=Pester|first=Lauren|work="EOnline"|date=2014-07-25|access-date=2018-07-06|dead-url=no|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180702093828/https://www.eonline.com/uk/news/563386/arrow-at-comic-con-get-scoop-on-a-two-hour-flash-crossover-oliver-and-felicity-s-romance-and-more|archive-date=2018-07-02|language=en-US}}</ref>。馬克·古根海姆表示本季將繼續探索「[[快手_(漫畫)|快手]]」{{le|西婭·奎恩|Thea Queen}}和[[黑金絲雀|「黑金絲雀」勞蕾爾·蘭斯]]的故事，特別是西婭·奎恩與父親{{le|馬爾科姆·梅林 (綠箭宇宙)|Malcolm Merlyn (Arrowverse)|馬爾科姆·梅林}}之間的關係<ref name="HR" />。此外，本季將揭示[[綠箭俠|「綠箭俠」奧利佛·昆恩]]與[[費莉西蒂·史莫克|費莉西蒂·史莫克]]確定關係之後的情感經歷<ref name="HR" />。馬克·古根海姆還透露[[布蘭登·勞斯|布蘭登·勞斯]]飾演的[[原子俠_(雷·帕爾默)|雷·帕爾默]]將影響奧利佛·昆恩的生活，為本季增添幽默元素<ref name="HR" />。

在聖地牙哥國際漫畫展上，製作組透露本季將揭示費莉西蒂·史莫克的過去經歷，以及她在[[麻省理工學院|麻省理工學院]]的生活<ref name="Pester" />。8月，馬克·古根海姆表示會在本季第五集〈費莉西蒂的秘密〉中引入費莉西蒂的母親{{le|唐娜·史莫克|Donna Smoak}}<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.ew.com/article/2014/08/18/arrow-felicity-backstory-season-3/|title='Arrow' changes title of Felicity's backstory episode|last=Abrams|first=Natalie|work="[[Entertainment_Weekly|Entertainment Weekly]]"|date=2014-08-18|access-date=2018-07-09|dead-url=no|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180710102834/http://www.ew.com/article/2014/08/18/arrow-felicity-backstory-season-3/|archive-date=2018-07-10|language=en-US}}</ref>。他還表示[[科林·唐納|科林·唐納]]在本季中回歸客串出演{{le|湯米·梅林|Tommy Merlyn}}<ref name="Kreisberg" />。預告片顯示本季的主要反派角色為[[拉斯·奧·古|拉斯·奧·古]]<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/live-feed/arrow-season-3-villain-ras-al-ghul-721453|title=Comic-Con: 'Arrow' Reveals Season 3 Villain (Video)|last=Ng|first=Philiana|work=[[The_Hollywood_Reporter|The Hollywood Reporter]]|date=2014-07-26|access-date=2018-07-09|dead-url=no|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160924151524/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/live-feed/arrow-season-3-villain-ras-al-ghul-721453|archive-date=2016-09-24|language=en-US}}</ref>。

